# Libera.Chat trust rules: <nick> <host_glob>
# On Libera the identified-to-services signal is 330 (RPL_WHOISACCOUNT), not
# Azzurra's 307 — bot.py handles both. vjt's Libera account cloak is user/vjt,
# which services assign ONLY to the account holder, so the host-glob alone is a
# strong gate (the WHOIS-verify is belt-and-suspenders).
vjt user/vjt
